data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home nestled in the highly sought-after Saddle Ridge community of Farragut, TN. Situated in a quiet cul-de-sac, this residence offers both privacy and accessibility to the best of suburban living. As you enter, the gleaming hardwood floors throughout the main level instantly capture your attention, setting a tone of elegance and warmth. The spacious eat-in kitchen, updated with sparkling quartz countertops, serves as the heart of the home - perfect for intimate family dinners or entertaining guests. The built-in shelves in the living room offer a blend of functionality and aesthetics, while the bonus room provides that extra space you've always desired - be it for entertainment, a play area, or a home gym. For those working from home, the dedicated office space ensures productivity and peace. Ascend to the upper level to find plush carpeting, ensuring a cozy atmosphere in all four generously-sized bedrooms. The master suite, complete with an ensuite bathroom, promises rest and relaxation.But that's not all! The expansive walk-in crawl space mirrors the size of a basement, offering a plethora of storage or potential for future personalization. Outdoors, the community presents amenities designed for recreation and relaxation. Dive into the refreshing community pool on hot summer days, or engage in a friendly tennis match at the courts.  Education is paramount, and this home is ideally positioned with access to some of Farragut's top-rated schools. Whether you're raising a family or planning to, this is a place where memories are made and dreams are realized. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a slice of Farragut's finest. Schedule your showing today!
